HEADWORD: perfumed
<hw>per"fumed</hw> <pr>(p⟦etil⟧r"f⟦umac⟧md)</pr> <pos>adj.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Filled or impregnated with perfume; <as>as,
<ex>perfumed</ex> stationery; a <ex>perfumed</ex>
boudoir</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> scented.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having a natural fragrance; <as>as, the
